{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775809247024,"sessionID":"ses_289858378ffe8pgoe8n4OXP7zD","part":{"id":"prt_d767ab2cd001iyqSon4DIdryvj","messageID":"msg_d767aac1b001ap0JfrhTwDL1dO","sessionID":"ses_289858378ffe8pgoe8n4OXP7zD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_0f9dbefe433d4bbdb66f4d97","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: 为 CodeInterpreter Custom Resource Definition 创建 Go 类型定义，与 AR-001 共享 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包中的公共类型（`TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`）。\n5: \n6: ## 元信息\n7: - **Module**: pkg/apis\n8: - **Language**: Go\n9: - **Size**: S\n10: \n11: ## 状态\n12: - [ ] 提案审查\n13: - [ ] 实现\n14: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 14 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## 概述\n为 CodeInterpreter Custom Resource Definition 创建 Go 类型定义，与 AR-001 共享 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包中的公共类型（`TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`）。\n\n## 元信息\n- **Module**: pkg/apis\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n\n## 状态\n- [ ] 提案审查\n- [ ] 实现\n- [ ] 验证","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775809247004,"end":1775809247022}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775809248305,"sessionID":"ses_289858378ffe8pgoe8n4OXP7zD","part":{"id":"prt_d767ab7a8001dxTtC0QV2PE0Ow","messageID":"msg_d767aac1b001ap0JfrhTwDL1dO","sessionID":"ses_289858378ffe8pgoe8n4OXP7zD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_8c9e395797f541b7a98e2fab","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: 为 AgentRuntime Custom Resource Definition 创建 Go 类型定义，作为 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的核心 API 基石。\n5: \n6: ## 元信息\n7: - **Module**: pkg/apis\n8: - **Language**: Go\n9: - **Size**: S\n10: \n11: ## 目的\n12: AgentRuntime CRD 是 AgentCube 的核心自定义资源，用于声明式地定义 AI Agent 沙箱的运行环境模板。本变更将在 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 下创建完整的 Go 类型定义，使 Kubernetes API Server 能够识别和管理 AgentRuntime 资源，并为后续的 WorkloadManager 控制器、client-go 生成代码和 CLI/SDK 提供类型基础。\n13: \n14: ## 范围\n15: \n16: ### 包含\n17: 1. **包结构** — 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 目录及 `doc.go`、`register.go`、`groupversion_info.go`\n18: 2. **核心类型** — `AgentRuntime`、`AgentRuntimeSpec`、`AgentRuntimeStatus`、`AgentRuntimeList`\n19: 3. **嵌套类型** — `SandboxTemplate`（嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`）、`TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`\n20: 4. **Kubebuilder 标记** — `+genclient`、`+kubebuilder:subresource:status`、`+kubebuilder:printcolumn`、字段验证和默认值标记\n21: 5. **Scheme 注册** — GroupVersion `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`、SchemeBuilder、AddToScheme\n22: 6. **DeepCopy 生成** — `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`（通过 `controller-gen object` 生成）\n23: \n24: ### 不包含\n25: - CRD YAML 文件生成（由 `make gen-crd` 在 `make generate` 中产出）\n26: - client-go 客户端代码生成（由 `make gen-client` 产出，依赖本变更的类型定义）\n27: - Controller/Reconciler 实现（后续变更）\n28: - CodeInterpreter CRD 类型定义（同属 `runtime/v1alpha1` 但为独立变更项）\n29: \n30: ## 类型定义概要\n31: \n32: ```\n33: AgentRuntime (namespaced CRD)\n34: ├── Spec: AgentRuntimeSpec\n35: │   ├── targetPort: []TargetPort\n36: │   │   ├── pathPrefix: string (optional)\n37: │   │   ├── name: string (optional)\n38: │   │   ├── port: uint32 (required)\n39: │   │   └── protocol: ProtocolType (default: HTTP, enum: HTTP|HTTPS)\n40: │   ├── podTemplate: *SandboxTemplate (required)\n41: │   │   ├── labels: map[string]string (optional)\n42: │   │   ├── annotations: map[string]string (optional)\n43: │   │   └── spec: corev1.PodSpec (required)\n44: │   ├── sessionTimeout: *metav1.Duration (required, default: 15m)\n45: │   └── maxSessionDuration: *metav1.Duration (required, default: 8h)\n46: └── Status: AgentRuntimeStatus\n47:     └── conditions: []metav1.Condition (optional)\n48: ```\n49: \n50: ## 影响分析\n51: \n52: ### 直接影响\n53: | 组件 | 影响 | 说明 |\n54: |------|------|------|\n55: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` | 新增 | 类型定义、Scheme 注册、DeepCopy 生成文件 |\n56: | `go.mod` | 依赖确认 | 需确保 `k8s.io/api`、`k8s.io/apimachinery` v0.34.1 已引入 |\n57: | `Makefile` | 无变更 | `generate`、`gen-crd`、`gen-client` 目标已存在 |\n58: \n59: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n60: | 组件 | 依赖关系 |\n61: |------|----------|\n62: | `client-go/` | `make gen-client` 读取本变更的类型定义生成 Typed Client、Informer、Lister |\n63: | CRD YAML | `make gen-crd` 从 kubebuilder 标记生成 `config/crd/bases/` 下的 YAML |\n64: | WorkloadManager | 通过 Informer/Lister 消费 AgentRuntime 资源，解析 SandboxTemplate 创建沙箱 |\n65: | CLI/SDK | 通过 client-go 生成的代码与 AgentRuntime CR 交互 |\n66: | Helm Chart | 部署时安装生成的 CRD YAML |\n67: \n68: ### 无影响的组件\n69: - Router（session-routing）— 不直接依赖 CRD 类型\n70: - Session Store（Redis/Valkey）— 存储层独立\n71: - Agentd（idle cleanup）— 通过 store 接口交互，不依赖 API 类型\n72: - PicoD（code execution）— 沙箱内组件，与 CRD 定义无关\n73: \n74: ## 备选方案\n75: \n76: ### 方案 A：直接在 `pkg/apis` 中定义（已选）\n77: **优点**：符合 Kubernetes 项目惯例（controller-runtime、kube-builder 标准布局）；与 `make gen-client` 和 `controller-gen` 工具链无缝集成；类型定义与代码生成标记同位。\n78: **缺点**：无显著缺点。\n79: \n80: ### 方案 B：使用 API Machinery 的 `runtime.Unknown` 动态类型\n81: **优点**：无需预定义类型，灵活性高。\n82: **缺点**：失去编译期类型安全；无法使用 kubebuilder 验证标记；client-go 代码生成器无法工作；与 AgentCube 已有的类型驱动设计不兼容。**否决**。\n83: \n84: ### 方案 C：将类型定义放在独立的 `api/` 顶层目录\n85: **优点**：与 `pkg/` 分离，更清晰的公共 API 边界。\n86: **缺点**：与项目现有约定（Go packages under `pkg/`）不一致；需要调整 Makefile 中的 controller-gen 路径参数；增加维护成本。**否决**。\n87: \n88: ### 方案 D：使用 Protocol Buffers 定义 API 类型\n89: **优点**：语言无关；gRPC 原生支持。\n90: **缺点**：Kubernetes CRD 生态基于 Go struct + kubebuilder 标记；需要额外的 proto-to-CRD 转换工具链；与现有 agent-sandbox 项目的 `corev1.PodSpec` 嵌入模式不兼容。**否决**。\n91: \n92: ## 验收标准\n93: 1. `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n94: 2. `make generate` 成功生成 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 且 `git diff --exit-code` 通过\n95: 3. `AgentRuntime` 类型的 GroupVersionKind 为 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, Kind=AgentRuntime`\n96: 4. GVR resource 名称为 `agentruntimes`\n97: 5. `SessionTimeout` 默认值为 `15m`，`MaxSessionDuration` 默认值为 `8h`\n98: 6. `SandboxTemplate.Spec` 类型为 `corev1.PodSpec` 且为必填字段\n99: 7. Status subresource 已启用（`+kubebuilder:subresource:status`）\n100: 8. `kubectl get agentruntimes` 输出包含 `Age` 列\n101: \n102: ## 状态\n103: - [ ] 提案审查\n104: - [ ] 实现\n105: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 105 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## 概述\n为 AgentRuntime Custom Resource Definition 创建 Go 类型定义，作为 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的核心 API 基石。\n\n## 元信息\n- **Module**: pkg/apis\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n\n## 目的\nAgentRuntime CRD 是 AgentCube 的核心自定义资源，用于声明式地定义 AI Agent 沙箱的运行环境模板。本变更将在 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 下创建完整的 Go 类型定义，使 Kubernetes API Server 能够识别和管理 AgentRuntime 资源，并为后续的 WorkloadManager 控制器、client-go 生成代码和 CLI/SDK 提供类型基础。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n1. **包结构** — 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 目录及 `doc.go`、`register.go`、`groupversion_info.go`\n2. **核心类型** — `AgentRuntime`、`AgentRuntimeSpec`、`AgentRuntimeStatus`、`AgentRuntimeList`\n3. **嵌套类型** — `SandboxTemplate`（嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`）、`TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`\n4. **Kubebuilder 标记** — `+genclient`、`+kubebuilder:subresource:status`、`+kubebuilder:printcolumn`、字段验证和默认值标记","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775809248293,"end":1775809248303}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775809249681,"sessionID":"ses_289858378ffe8pgoe8n4OXP7zD","part":{"id":"prt_d767abd14001VKaYeP2oAB6y4Q","messageID":"msg_d767aac1b001ap0JfrhTwDL1dO","sessionID":"ses_289858378ffe8pgoe8n4OXP7zD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_4024d7f5d09a4f2a9872c40f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package v1alpha1\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \tcorev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"\n5: \tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n6: )\n7: \n8: type ProtocolType string\n9: \n10: const (\n11: \tProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n12: \tProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n13: )\n14: \n15: type AuthModeType string\n16: \n17: const (\n18: \tAuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n19: \tAuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n20: )\n21: \n22: type TargetPort struct {\n23: \tPathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n24: \tName       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n25: \tPort       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n26: \tProtocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n27: }\n28: \n29: // +genclient\n30: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n31: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n32: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n33: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n34: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n35: \n36: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n37: \tmetav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n38: \tmetav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n39: \n40: \tSpec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n41: \tStatus CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n42: }\n43: \n44: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n45: \tPorts              []TargetPort                    `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n46: \tTemplate           *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n47: \tSessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration                `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n48: \tMaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration                `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n49: \tWarmPoolSize       *int32                          `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n50: \tAuthMode           AuthModeType                    `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n51: }\n52: \n53: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n54: \tConditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n55: \tReady      bool               `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n56: }\n57: \n58: type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n59: \tLabels           map[string]string             `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n60: \tAnnotations      map[string]string             `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n61: \tRuntimeClassName *string                       `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n62: \tImage            string                        `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n63: \tImagePullPolicy  corev1.PullPolicy             `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n64: \tImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n65: \tEnvironment      []corev1.EnvVar               `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n66: \tCommand          []string                      `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n67: \tArgs             []string                      `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n68: \tResources        corev1.ResourceRequirements   `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n69: }\n70: \n71: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n72: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n73: \n74: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n75: \tmetav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n76: \tmetav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n77: \tItems           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n78: }\n79: \n80: func init() {\n81: \tSchemeBuilder.Register(&CodeInterpreter{}, &CodeInterpreterList{})\n82: }\n\n(End of file - total 82 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package v1alpha1\n\nimport (\n\tcorev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"\n\tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n)\n\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n\tProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n\tProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n\tAuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n\tAuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go","time":{"start":1775809249661,"end":1775809249679}}}}
